                            <div style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #3b82f6; margin-bottom: 4px;">1+</div>
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Yıl Deneyim</div>
